website_summaries.verdict: Extra protein compared to most other types of dry food. Different formulas for cats with different needs.
pros: Manufacturer offers four types of foods, including high protein or hairball control
Owners like how small size of kibble works well for many sizes of cats
cons: Cats tended to be hungrier between feedings with this food
Some customers say their cats dislike taste

customer_reviews.title: Sensitive tummy approved!
customer_reviews.text: Ever since we got our cat from the shelter (as a kitten), he struggled with a respiratory virus, and a sensitive digestive system. Not sure if they are related, but after we got his sneezing under control with supplements, he continued struggling with the tummy issues (lots of throwing up). He went from throwing up once a day (sometimes twice) to once a week within the first week of introducing the Nutro (Salmon flavor) food. Not sure if it's the grain free factor or the fish, but we love it and he loves it even more :)
customer_reviews.author: Berries
